name: CLEANER GLASS MIROSPRAY DCS
description: Glass Cleaner DCS. Cleans windows, mirrors, chrome, stainless steel, Plexiglas plastic surfaces, and much more. Streak-free formula tackles the toughest cleaning jobs. Two 1-gallon containers of concentrate make 136 RTU gallons. Comes with a Saf T Flo fitment top to create a closed loop self venting system.

name: CLEANER GLASS MIROZERO VOC FREE 32 OZ
description: Glass Cleaner. Ready to use, streak-free cleaning. Mir-O-Zero is 100% V.O.C. (volatile organic compound) free—no ammonia, alcohol, butyl, or solvents. Great for windows, metal, plastic, fiberglass, and plexiglass surfaces. Spray directly on surface to be cleaned, wipe dry with a clean cloth.

name: DETERGENT BAR GLASS LO SUDS 1 GAL
description: Bar Glass Cleaner. Complete glass sanitizing for any bar. Sparkling clean glasses help beer look better and produce a better head. Sell more beer per keg for increased profits. Choose convenient premeasured packets or economical bulk jars.

name: CLEANER GLASS MIROSPRAY RTU 1 GAL
description: Glass Cleaner. Heavy-duty glass cleaner. Ready to use formula. Non-streaking formula removes dirt, smoke and grime from all surfaces quickly and easily. Great for windows, mirrors, Formica, porcelain, table tops, steam tables, sneeze shields, bar tops, plastic coated menus, and more. For glass and mirrors use a soft, lint-free cloth for best results. Cleans fingerprints and light grease.

name: CLEANER GLASS MIROSPRAY ORIGINAL 32 OZ
description: Glass Cleaner. Cleans windows, mirrors, chrome, stainless steel, plexiglas plastic surfaces and much more; available in four formulas. Aerosol (1J604) is a ready-to-use ammonia-free, high-foaming formula that won’t streak or leave a film. Heavy duty glass cleaner (1J331) is an ammoniated, clear blue formula for tough cleaning jobs in a ready-to-use gallon size. Mir-O-Zero (1J983) is 100% VOC (volatile organic compound) free—no ammonia, alcohol, butyl or solvents.

name: BOTTLE REFILL MIROSPRAY 32OZ
description: Spray Bottle. Empty, labeled bottles for Mir-O-Spray products. 32 oz capacity.

name: CLEANER GLASS TWIST N FILL 1 LTR
description: Cleaner. Cleans windows, mirrors, display cases, fixtures and tabletops. Each bottle mixes with water to make 37 ready-to-use gallons.

name: CLEANER GLASS MIR-O-SPRAY AERO 19 OZ
description: Glass Cleaner. Dissolves dirt and grime leaves a shine. Cleans and polishes windows, mirrors, sneeze guards, showcases, chrome, stainless steel, light fixtures and more. Choose from foam-action aerosol or ready-to-use liquid. 10 oz, USDA: C1.

name: CLEANER GLASS WINDEX W/TRIGGER 32OZ BLU
description: CLEANER GLASS WINDEX W/TRIGGER 32OZ BLU. Leaves glass and other surfaces sparkling. Institutional strength formula starts cleaning before wiping begins. Exclusive Ammonia-D® removes dirt without streaking or filming.

name: CLEANER WINDOW ARROW 1 GAL
description: Cleaner. Concentrated glass and surface cleaner, quick drying. Cuts through smoke, grease and grime. Anti-fog and anti-static, can be used on car windshields.
